title: [Mist Harbor, Vineyard]
description: Trellises laden with verdant grapevines stretch outward from the gate in a roughly triangular shape towards the distant cliffs.  Tufts of pale yellow grass, surrounded by darker, moist grasses, rise beneath each of the vines and lift their blade-like ends towards the plump purple grapes that ripen in the sun.
